message: Let's start fair. I'll take 90% and you get 10%.  What do you say?
I'll give you a slightly better deal. You can have 60% and I'll take 40%.
I'm willing to compromise, but 60/40 is still too much in your favor. I'll take 7200, leaving you with 2800.  Let's meet in the middle.
I'm not willing to give up more than 35%. You can have 65% if you want.
